name: SuperPA.net
overview:
SuperPA.Net, Inc. operates as an Internet service provider for residential and corporate clients in South Central Pennsylvania. It offers Internet access, networking, e-commerce, and computer repair services. The company also provides dedicated connections, dialup access, wireless access, firewalls and security, digital subscriber line services, business integrated services digital network, and Web hosting services. In addition, SuperPA.Net offers Web development services, which include consultation, graphic design and production, site development, e-commerce solutions, interactive solutions, site hosting and maintenance, promotion and marketing, and personal services.

The company was founded in 1998 and is based in Gettysburg, Pennsylvania. As of April 9, 2008, SuperPA.net, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Double Dog Communications.
